description:
Bellandur residents who love playing sports or wanna try out sports should definitely walk into PlayMania, located very close to the Bellandur lake.
They offer not just one sport but 4 Sports, Badminton, Football, Table Tennis and Volleyball.
They have 2 Football turfs at the venue laid out with Astro turf and they are operational from 6 am in the morning until midnight. They also have Badminton courts at the venue. There are 4 Badminton courts made out of synthetic surfaces which supports professional play. These synthetic surfaces are of High quality and the lighting is also good. 
You could also enjoy playing Table Tennis at the venue as they have a table available. 

It is hardly 10 minutes away from the Central Mall, Bellandur by Car/Motorcycle.
They also provide basic amenities like Parking and Washrooms.

4 International class BWF approved wooden badminton courts with high luminosity lighting. Located on Sarjapur Main Road adjacent to Wipro's headquarters, near Cafe Coffee Day. Non Marking shoes only allowed on the courts. Users can obtain these at the facility on rent.

BADMINTON RULES AND REGULATIONS AT STAR BADMINTON

1) We request the customers the carry the shoes and change it only at the courts.Customers shouldn't wear and use the Badminton shoes outside of the Badminton courts.
2) Star Badminton is providing international standard flooring for the customers and hence are strictly restricting the customers to use any other Non Marking shoes like tennis shoes or Football shoes.
3) Please note that only Badminton Non marking shoes are allowed to use.
4) All persons using the badminton facility at the STAR BADMINTON ACADEMY at their own risk and sole responsibility the management accepts no liability/death or any associated accident from the same.
5) No clothing, valuables or articles should be left by members/students. The management takes no responsibility or liability for the loss of the same.
6) Every player should leave the court immediately after use.
7) Consumption of food and alcohol in the facility is not permitted.
8) Smoking is prohibited in the facility.
9) T-shirt and athletic non marking shoes must be worn at all times.
10) Attendants, Bearers, Drivers, Servants and pets are not permitted to enter the playing area.
11) Any damage to the court while playing is chargeable.
12) Please sign in the register before using the facility.

addInfo:
Non-Marking badminton shoes compulsory for people willing to play Badminton.

Come and play / eat and refresh 24 hrs @ Active Arena - A unique Sports and entertainment centre. 

We have 3 fields of 5 a-side football which doubles up as a 7 a-side and 9 a-side.The turf is imported from Belgium and is FIFA approved.

The MUST SEE uniquely built Badminton Drome has BWF approved flooring which gives a great play experience. Lighting levels of 310 lumens are in line with BWF's amateaur game lighting requirement. Superb ventilation ensures optimum temperatures and keeps away humidity and sweat smell. 

The first of its kind (in Bangalore) adventure sports activity and wall climb is suitable for ages 4 onwards. Try walking on the rope at 30 feet high, of course with helmets and harness.

Try out the special Active Namma Cross Fit Gym. 

Soon to come Indoor cricket, Volleyball, Archery, Skating, Zip-line, Cricket Simulator, Shooting, TT, Snooker, Fusball, VR games, Children's play area
description:
Located in Marathahalli, Active Arena is a 24-hours open venue which hosts facilities for Football, Badminton, Basketball and Volleyball. 
The Football turfs at the venue is of High quality Astro turf of FIFA standards and is much suited for 5/7/9 a-side Football games. 
They have 4 Badminton courts laid out at the venue and all these Badminton courts have PU Flooring which makes these surfaces synthetic in nature. The lighting facilities in the arena are top notch and supports a great play, professionally and for fun as well. 
You can also bring in your folks to watch your game or host matches at this arena, as they have a gallery stationed out for the viewers. 

Directions:

If you are finding it hard to locate the venue, locate J.P Morgan or Adobe Systems in Marathahalli, take the road opposite to Adobe systems, you will find "Croma" showroom on the right, take the first left and move further, you will find Active Arena in the end.

Go ahead and have some fun at the venue and don't forget to rate the venue on the app.
